Dialogue.2A11CE8F43A451F7E49820996C5EAB74_DB7CBEB: Ah! Quickly! Before it's too late!
Dialogue.3A051E0349A7CA93F75875A0446D283D_DB7CBEB: Aw, man. Cut down that flinger.
Dialogue.FAC9289E496AF24EEAD6BAAAA0043E2E_DB7CBEB: Can't kill you when you're dead.
Dialogue.E6A3530948D5F329689208B0A92F2EC0_DB7CBEB: Come on, bring back the ninja!
Dialogue.9FBBF6B84F6E60620025809CD39D188B_7023BF2: Could use some R and R…
Dialogue.80B291C14A1B6510ED6D3899A4AC1219_DB7CBEB: Death from above!  And all that good stuff…
Dialogue.02AA9F764A0B647494504993C4D44372_DB7CBEB: Did somebody call for a master?
Dialogue.1D20220047B9DC89CBB5F9B2C77C65DC_7023BF2: Got a rift in my sights.
Dialogue.6A0D81F74D81B403AD53BC840FDE4CD0_DB7CBEB: Hey! Hey! Dead ninja over here! Come on!
Dialogue.027068F744FB19BBD2D600B8FB6CBC43_DB7CBEB: Hoo hoo, it's on for real!
Dialogue.B8F1682544626A4AFDA99389331A5868_DB7CBEB: How'd you know I love presents?  C'mon, man…
Dialogue.B368B841429095872829098B63C70F42_7023BF2: Huh. Usually I'm the other guy.
Dialogue.015913124757A76EA09CC0BBE6765245_DB7CBEB: I'm down… but I'm not out.
Dialogue.CDE1807B43F8A6A1A1082FB37EAEA396_DB7CBEB: I'm too young and too beautiful!
Dialogue.599FFBE9408D1B4F57EAE0A37E6584EF_DB7CBEB: Losing blood. But I still look good.
Dialogue.F69AA63C40BCDBE29B11DDB24A750DBE_7023BF2: No one is impressed by you.
Dialogue.7E9E081C42079EB1B909F492DF6B6D44_DB7CBEB: No, no. Please, accept a gift.
Dialogue.0258B2E7426A790AE1DD978EB37EBDF9_DB7CBEB: No, thank you. No, thank you!
Dialogue.73E0FDC34BBF036AF5CDF3A5B9390CE6_DB7CBEB: Now don't get excited, y'all gonna get a turn.
Dialogue.7D44CA264E1EE544C8B9298A56487315_DB7CBEB: Now that right there could cause some trouble.
Dialogue.1C78C9AD406BD839F5DF998FB4544E5D_DB7CBEB: Now that's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue.D588C13C4430E627720784A88B8DD409_DB7CBEB: Oh! Did somebody call for a dragon master?
Dialogue.8F08B9844DD41231E273028263B2CAE5_DB7CBEB: Oh, come on! You forget about me?
Dialogue.5CCB821040206DDEA4EB4BA510D58E7D_DB7CBEB: Oh, this? This now belongs to you.
Dialogue.553860E247D0131EFAE00C91D36B4669_7023BF2: One for you. Oh yeah, one for you. One for you. Oh yeah, not forgettin' you!
Dialogue.6A74AB4E40C79A7AACD935BC2F340C19_DB7CBEB: Oooh, you better believe we're ready.
Dialogue.BAD63494414397B9E8FE5DBA24FCAD6E_DB7CBEB: Oooh. I didn't get you anything.
Dialogue.1CD66C82423CAE20AD7700926065DD16_DB7CBEB: Please. Accept a gift. I insist.
Dialogue.BD7DF84149E4A56E30D2D4A6AB6A2A68_DB7CBEB: Post-apocalyptic storm ninja, like I do.
Dialogue.13CF64184F310F7800E2E98C5754A541_DB7CBEB: Sharp blades, sharp focus… smoke bombs.
Dialogue.E96B862D4E5ECABF834CB3B1963988FC_7023BF2: Should I be suspicious or flattered.
Dialogue.2471F6304C52F5EA36BC33A92DCACB04_7023BF2: Society requires rules, you little monster.
Dialogue.09B87D6E4A6C1CF8A9147D8E113E0D94_DB7CBEB: Speak softly, stab quietly... you know, enjoy the little things.
Dialogue.AE22E15E4FB35A39E43888852F56C713_7023BF2: That is an act of aggression.
Dialogue.9F122F584A8E51ED759226ACDF143736_DB7CBEB: The master. And don't you forget it.
Dialogue.16E8C7A741BAC55BE7EEE2AB62C892A0_7023BF2: This fun for you? It won't be for long!
Dialogue.C1A6C0D1434600A4F2D9F29FBFD141BE_DB7CBEB: Uh oh. taker… coming for me!
Dialogue.B109508B4ED949A24C717AB30CCE9D5D_DB7CBEB: Who saw that? That was good, right?
Dialogue.DFCB966240CA697BA9EAC09B876E1932_7023BF2: Whoa! You'd make an amazing pet.
Dialogue.31CF5037469F32F5EEE66096DAE090AB_DB7CBEB: Yeah. Storm's not gonna like that, but, ah, I don't care.
Dialogue.B68D5F9040F11060ADB39DAD33580FA6_DB7CBEB: Yo, Smasher. You're messing with the wrong fort.
Dialogue.479F12064DA5AE4BF210E5AE4040A9F9_DB7CBEB: You sure you want to do this?
Dialogue.96967D454161F7CFE87C0FBAD1C5722E_DB7CBEB: You're not on the list.  But now you are.
